Tech Stack: React 18, TypeScript, Lucide React (icon library), Storybook, Vitest.

Naming Convention: Components use PascalCase, directories use kebab-case.

Export Convention: Use Named Exports only, Default Export is prohibited.

File Structure: Each component must include index.ts (exports), ComponentName.tsx (logic), ComponentName.stories.tsx (stories), __tests__ (tests).

Text: No Chinese characters in comments or code.

Git Workflow: After completing tasks, DO NOT commit automatically. Let the user review changes and commit manually. Only execute commit and push when the user explicitly requests it.

